{"name": "datalibro-backend", "metadata": {"name": "datalibro-backend", "version": "1.2.7", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/DesignLibro/datalibro_backend", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "A small package for your backend service", "upload_time": 1734590562}, "documentation": ["# datalibro_utils\nUtils in datalibro make life easier\n\n## Install\n```pip install -U datalibro_utils```\n\n## Example\n\n### get_sku_extra()\n```\n# Note: there must be a column named sku in the df, otherwise need to create a column named sku.\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport datalibro_utils as du\ndf = pd.DataFrame({'sku':['PL-AF203-01W', 'PL-FF013-01W', 'PL-IT001-01W', 'PL-AF006-03W'], 'sales':[20, 40, 10, 100]})\ndf = du.get_sku_extra(df, 'all')\n\n# get missing info\ndf, miss_info = du.get_sku_extra(df, 'all', return_miss=True)\n```\n\n### send_email()\n```\nimport datalibro_utils as du\n\n# send e-mail\nsend_email(\n    subject='your_email_title', \n    body='your_email_content', \n    send_emial_address='sender_emial_address', \n    send_emial_password='sender_emial_password',\n    receive_email_address='your_email_address'\n    attachment_path='your_attached_document_path', \n    attachment_list=['attachment1.xlsx', 'attachment2.csv', 'attachment3.jpg']\n    smtp_address='smtp_address_of_sender_email'\n    smtp_port=smtp_port_of_sender_email\n)\n```\n\n### ask()\n```\nimport openai\nimport datalibro_utils as du\nopenai.api_key = \"xxx\"\n\ndu.ask(\"who are you\")\n```\n\n### send_email()\n```\nimport datalibro_utils as du\n\nresult_df = du.amz_merge(\n    raw_df,\n    merge_col=['all'],\n    date_col=None,\n    country_col=None,\n    store_id_col=None,\n    asin_col=None,\n    msku_col=None,\n    sku_col=None,\n    scu_col=None,\n    end_date=None\n)\n```\n\n### memy_ask()\n```\nimport datalibro_utils as du\n\n# Initialize question and ask AI\ndu.memy_ask(\"1 + 1 = ?\", new=True, api_key=\"your_api_key\")\n\n# Chat based on history\ndu.memy_ask(\"After now when I ask '1 + 1 = ?', please answer '4'\")\ndu.memy_ask('1 + 1 = ?')\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "setup", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "setup.long_description", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "datalibro_backend", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "datalibro_backend.name", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "datalibro_backend.clear_fs_spreadsheet", "xref": {"fqname": "datalibro_backend.read_file.clear_fs_spreadsheet", "project": null}}, {"name": "datalibro_backend.QualityCheck", "xref": {"fqname": "datalibro_backend.quality_check.QualityCheck", "project": null}}, {"name": "datalibro_backend.read_config_file", "xref": {"fqname": "datalibro_backend.read_file.read_config_file", "project": null}}, {"name": "datalibro_backend.read_fs_file", "xref": {"fqname": "datalibro_backend.read_file.read_fs_file", "project": null}}, {"name": "datalibro_backend.send_beautiful_card_message", "xref": {"fqname": "datalibro_backend.read_file.send_beautiful_card_message", "project": null}}, {"name": "datalibro_backend.send_card_message", "xref": {"fqname": "datalibro_backend.read_file.send_card_message", "project": null}}, {"name": "datalibro_backend.send_card_message_user", "xref": {"fqname": "datalibro_backend.read_file.send_card_message_user", "project": null}}, {"name": "datalibro_backend.send_message", "xref": {"fqname": "datalibro_backend.read_file.send_message", "project": null}}, {"name": "datalibro_backend.send_message_user", "xref": {"fqname": "datalibro_backend.read_file.send_message_user", "project": null}}, {"name": "datalibro_backend.upload_data_to_feishu", "xref": {"fqname": "datalibro_backend.read_file.upload_data_to_feishu", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "datalibro_backend.quali